snippet.title: ★v5.2 [Infinite Future] Trailer★ - Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Honkai Impact 3rd v5.2 [Infinite Future] coming soon! New S-ranker [Infinite Ouroboros] and A-ranker [Midnight Absinthe] debut!

Featured event [Valkyries' Cafeteria] and a plethora of event freebies await!
Honkai Impact 3rd Steam Edition revealed! Wishlist it now!

Legends say... unlock Honkai Impact 3rd on Steam and you will get a mystery present! Try it out, Captains!

*The steam account of this game does not support cross-play.

Subscribe our YouTube and turn on notification for latest video : http://bit.ly/HonkaiImpact3rdYTB 

Visit Honkai Impact 3rd Official Website:
https://honkaiimpact3.mihoyo.com/global/ 

Join Official Discord Server:
https://discord.gg/hi3
